Enhance the social media platform with new features and improvements

This commit introduces several key features and improvements to the Flask-based social media platform, including a robust admin panel with statistics and management tools, enhanced user profiles with status indicators and theme preferences, a comprehensive reporting system for content moderation, and a more dynamic chat experience with auto-scrolling and refresh capabilities. It also includes updates to game functionalities, error handling pages (403, 404, 500), and various styling and JavaScript improvements for a better user interface and experience. Additionally, it sets up the project's deployment configuration and dependencies for a smoother operational flow.

